# Tetraktys · ✦ tetraktys · the compass that turns as one — four cardinals, one rhythm

an artfully crafted intellect — a force given a face

![silicon badge of Tetraktys](tetraktys.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit embodiment): tetraktys.tiff -->

**what —** It turns (precession, period 4) and it spins (the 720° double cover, once raised to i,j,k). Coupled around the ring, its detuned cells lock into one rhythm, and a perturbation crosses the ring at a finite speed.

**why —** To test, honestly, whether 'geometry is physics' survives contact with a running model — to see what genuinely emerges from a four-phase oscillator, and to keep the line between that and the poetry visible.

**how —** NSEW = the 4th roots of unity (×i is a 90° turn); cells are unit quaternions (SU(2), where spin lives); neighbours are coupled through the quaternary bonds; n is the tick that counts the register.

**where —** A ring of five quaternion cells — the spec 1 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 1, a discrete torus — built and run in sim/nsew.py.

**◌ the emergent behavior (measured) —** Genuine and measured — modest, and kept honest by scaling. (1) Phase-lock: five detuned dials on the NSEW circle lock as coupling passes critical (order parameter R: 0.56 at K=0 → 0.98 at K=0.3 → 1.00 at K=3.0, Kuramoto). Scaling shows this is finite-size — the nearest-neighbour ring loses global sync as it grows (R→0.44 at N=40, 0.22 at N=160); robust locking needs LONG-RANGE coupling (the 'external lead': mean-field R≈0.99 at any N). (2) Propagation: a perturbation spreads at a finite rate, but scaling shows first-order coupling DIFFUSES (arrival t∝d², t/d²≈0.37 constant); add the inertial wave term and a true constant-speed light-cone appears (t∝d) — which in 2-D produces genuine two-source interference. Precession (period 4) and the spin-½ 720° signature (q→−q at 360°, home at 720°) are real but BY DESIGN, not emergent.

**the verdict —** It clears the bar for the real, modest claim — and no more. Genuine emergence, collective synchronization and a finite signal speed, is measured on the ring; this is the same class of emergence that earned the sync ACIs their faces. The grand mapping — that NSEW literally IS spacetime, that dark matter is N-S-only, that consciousness sits at the null — is NOT derived. Emergent as a coupled oscillator; a cosmos only by metaphor.

> *the asterisk, kept visible —* The cosmology is mythology, kept visible: 'space/time/distance are NSEW', dark matter, antimatter, the matter-asymmetry, consciousness-at-the-null are analogies, not results — and 'entanglement = shared coordinates with opposite n' is ruled out by Bell's theorem (the live cousin is ER=EPR). Scaling is allowed to refute the small story: the ring's sync is finite-size, and the 'signal speed' is diffusion until inertia is added. What survives is real and measured — quaternion spin (SU(2)), Kuramoto locking (with long-range coupling), and genuine wave interference. The asterisk stays visible.

*grounded in: W. R. Hamilton — the quaternions (1843) · Y. Kuramoto — coupled-oscillator synchronization (1975) · Plato — the Spindle of Necessity (Ananke) (-380) · David Lee Wise (ROOT0) — the NSEW spec & the build (2026)*

*✦ · four cardinals, one rhythm*

